    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty\u2014it's like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied this car, and it's in truly pristine condition inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for total perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
